channel.title: Project DS - Public BETA soon!
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2ni5r0m.png[/img][/center]
Welcome to my current server development! I've been working on this server for the past few weeks solo coding all the work, but I am in need of some desperate help in order to get my server up and running for the public!
[b]Our current team![/b] -[i]destermino[/i] Special thank you for joining the team! Great inspiration on what type of graphics I'm looking for!
[b]What I'm currently looking for?[/b] I need some beta testers to be ready for the first launch! in order to sign up just drop a comment on this topic and a good reason for you to join, all the details on how to play will be given to you when you join.
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/15eb6fq.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2hn96js.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2q0t3yb.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2mgs9pl.jpg[/img] More details will be handed out very soon!
